{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_COR_220.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x20,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Cory. You're listening to the music box again?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x5a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yes... It's become like a daily routine for me now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Huh, I see... It really is a nice tune, though."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x5a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hey, what are you two doing here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Ah, hello Logy. We were listening to Cory's music box."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0xb,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I see, so that box was a music box."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0xb,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "A music box, huh..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0xb,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "This is a pretty nostalgic tune. I wonder how many years it's been since I heard it last?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "What...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Logy, you know this tune?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0xb,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Hm? Yeah. It's not exactly the same, but I heard it when I traveled for training."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Really!? Logy, can you please tell us more!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1f,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "We might figure something out about Cory's dad!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I'd... Like to ask as well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I heard this song in a country far to the east of here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "That reminds me, there were lots of people over there who wore clothes like yours..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "And? What else!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Do you... Know anything else?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Let's see... Also..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Hm, that's about it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Logy, thank you so much! You really helped!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Thank you... Very much..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "No problem. I'm glad I could help. Anyway, I'll get going now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "That's great, Cory. We got to hear all kinds of things!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Yes... He really did have a lot to tell us...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "So my people are in a country to the east... My dad could be in the east too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Um, Cory... Are you thinking about going to look for him?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "...I don't know. Not right now, at least..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "(It would get kind of lonely around here if Cory left this town...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "(But it would be to find her dad. I would need to support her decision, if she does...!)"
        }
    ]
}